text: The abbreviation CWU may refer to: *Central Washington University *China Women's University *Church Women United *Crowhurst railway station, East Sussex, National Rail station code *One of several Communication Workers' Unions, including: **Communication Workers Union of Australia **Communication Workers Union (Ireland) **Communication Workers Union (South Africa) **Communication Workers Union (Trinidad and Tobago) **Communication Workers Union (United Kingdom)
title: CWU
